{
  "stem": "17761.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 125.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In 10 minutes, the bridges explode, both bridges, with hundreds, perhaps thousands of people on the bridges.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With horses and wagons and tanks and ever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything went in the air, because they didn't want the Russian to get the bridges.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of the people jumped into the water, some didn't know to swim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some drowned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some-- it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw-- I saw the-- the explosions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't see what that-- we heard the-- the noises.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People crying, people yelling, everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And suddenly, there was silence, and all the German soldiers who were still in houses and streets and [INAUDIBLE], they start to the Dniester to find some way to get over the Dniester.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Naturally, that only few of them did-- could do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But meanwhile, youngsters of the ghetto took possession of the German armies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of them just shot a lot of soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some others took prisoners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We handed over to the Russian army between 20 and 30,000 prisoners from that area that we caught with the German armies.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Later, a monument was erected in Mogilev in memory of 11 partisans who sneaked in with the German army, in German uniforms, on those bridges, and started to throw hand grenades on the bridges.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And therefore, the Germans thought that the Russians are here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And therefore, they exploded the bridges.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so, the ghetto was saved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Those who remained in that ghetto were saved and continued to live.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's a-- a miracle in [NON-ENGLISH] that none of us can explain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If that would have taken two, three days more, I don't think that we could take this video today.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What was also amazing, we saw such an armies withdrawing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They will come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Russian army.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That must be something outstanding.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
